# Hugging Face token, used as the default for gated model downloads/generation
# (SD 3.5, FLUX.1-dev, etc.) when a request doesn't supply its own hf_token.
# Get one at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your token. .env is gitignored — never
# commit a real token.
HF_TOKEN=
